import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import { Dropdown,DropdownToggle, DropdownMenu, DropdownItem } from 'react-bootstrap';

function AppHeader() {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg">
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Corporate</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
          <Nav className="me-auto">
            <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#about">About</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#services">Services</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#works">Works</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#teams">Teams</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#testimonials">Testimonials</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#pricing">Pricing</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#blog">Blog</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#contact">Contact</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Dropdown >
                <Nav.DropdownToggle >Learn</Nav.DropdownToggle>
                <Nav.DropdownMenu >
                  <Nav.DropdownItem href="#">Learn React</Nav.DropdownItem>
                  {/* <Nav.DropdownItem divider /> */}
                  <Nav.DropdownItem href="#">Documentation</Nav.DropdownItem>
                  <Nav.DropdownItem href="#">Tutorials</Nav.DropdownItem>
                  <Nav.DropdownItem href="#">Courses</Nav.DropdownItem>
                </Nav.DropdownMenu>
            </Nav.Dropdown>

          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
}

export default AppHeader;
